reviewText: A waste of money.  The DVD was blurred and dark.  DON'T BOTHER WITH THIS DVD.  iT ISN'T WORTH IT AT ALL.

Good collection of a woman's power of endurance through various crisis in her life whether she be "whore", "heroine" or somewhere in the middle.  Sophia Loren is excellent in "Two Women" - her Oscar winning pwerformance.
